      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i was prescribed some antibiotics for this skin infection i had. i've only been on them for 3 days but the redness and swelling are totally gone now and i feel fine. is it okay if i stop taking them early? i dont really want to keep putting chemicals in my body if i dont need to anymore.",
