      "content": "but my doctor just gave me the prescription and didn't really explain why i had to finish the whole thing if the skin is already clear. it seems like a waste of medicine and i'm worried about the side effects from taking them for another week for no reason. if there's no more swelling or pain, isn't the infection technically gone?",
